&_nc_ohc=qBrMFV49s8UQ7kNvgG5Li76&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAEQRp_DkpjTOXweJHQB5pmaB1ySouHOOlg58YwPRMnBw&oe=66CDC0B8"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "cover.png", "id": "7957285167664031", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974670_7957285174330697_8761544827049069134_n.png?_nc_cat=111&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=bmloRQVifRoQ7kNvgGVwGBM&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYD00iOhvdWgLNmhIMwivy0lZAATMRRQy0uc1JduCxJXUA&oe=66CDADE9"}, "display_name": "Thief in the Colossus", "keywords": [], "long_description": "Description:\nStep into the shoes of a master thief in the thrilling VR game \"Thief in the Colossus.\" Your mission is to \"borrow\" precious items from an enormous, high-tech space, while avoiding detection by the colossal room owner. This immersive game offers an unparalleled blend of stealth, strategy, and futuristic adventure, set in a sprawling, technologically advanced environment.\n\nGame Features:\n\n    Immersive VR Experience:\n        Fully immerse yourself in a beautifully crafted, gigantic space with state-of-the-art VR graphics. Feel the tension as you navigate through vast rooms filled with high-tech gadgets and traps.\n\n    Stealth and Strategy:\n        Use your cunning and skills to outsmart the colossal room owner. Plan your heist meticulously, use shadows to your advantage, and deploy advanced tools to avoid detection.", "short_description": "Description:\nStep into the shoes of a master thief in the thrilling VR game \"Thief in the Colossus.\" Your mission is to \"borrow\" precious items from an enormous, high-tech space, while avoiding detection by the colossal room owner. This immersive game offers an unparalleled blend of stealth, strategy, and futuristic adventure, set in a sprawling, technologically advanced environment."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://sites.google.com/view/thief-in-the-colossus/privacy-policy", "developer_terms_